trans-unit.source: Represents a set of selected dates in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje zestaw zaznaczonych dat w <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Dates can be added to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.
trans-unit.target: Daty można dodać do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>właściwości <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>

trans-unit.source: Depending on the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, adding a date or a range to the SelectedDatesCollection may cause it to be cleared.
trans-unit.target: W zależności od wartości <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości, dodając datę lub zakres do SelectedDatesCollection może spowodować jej do wyczyszczenia.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectionMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists how <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode> affects the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: W poniższej tabeli wymieniono jak <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>wpływa na <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>Właściwości.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>

trans-unit.target: | CalendarSelectionMode | Wpływ na SelectedDates | |---------------------------|-----------------------------| | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>| Żadne opcje nie są dozwolone.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>

trans-unit.source: Setting <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A>, adding a date individually to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>, or using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A> will clear all previous values from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>.| |<xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>|Multiple non-contiguous ranges of dates can be selected.
trans-unit.target: Ustawienie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A>, dodając datę indywidualnie do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>lub przy użyciu <xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A>usunie wszystkie poprzednie wartości z <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>. | | <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode>| Można wybrać wiele zakresów nieciągłych dat.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarSelectionMode> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adding a date individually to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> or using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A> will not clear <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Dodawanie datę indywidualnie lub <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>przy użyciu <xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A>nie usunie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.SelectedDatesCollection.AddRange%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>

trans-unit.source: Setting <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A> will still clear <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>, but additional dates or ranges can then be added.
trans-unit.target: Ustawienie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A>nadal spowoduje wyczyszczenie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A>, ale następnie można dodać dodatkowe dane lub zakresy.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDates%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Calendar.SelectedDate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adding a range that includes some dates that are already selected or overlaps with another range results in the union of the ranges and does not cause an exception.|
trans-unit.target: Dodawanie zakresu, który zawiera niektóre daty, które zostały już wybrane lub nakładania się z innym zakresem wyniki w związku z zakresów i nie powoduje wyjątek. |
